rest_of_day_open: I see it as being similar to other weeks I have been having lately. There are some tasks that I wish to complete through next week and i would like to make some progress on them. I'm trying to use my time for self-improvement and I'm having difficulty doing that. I hope that I can shake my emotional slump soon and get my life back on track.
critical_positive: We both were people interested in learning about the stranger on the other end. i was curious about what they did and where they lived. It was nice learning about another person's life. We both had a good sense about balance in the conversation, and both of us got to learn about the other evenly.
critical_negative: There were no technical issues to speak of. The only issue was what I usually see in these video call where it's too easy to talk over another person. I find that for whatever reason, it is much too easy for the two participants to cut each other off. This leads to the two people stumbling over their speaking or a comment getting lost in the mix.

rest_of_day_open: It will be busy because I have some travel coming up with my 4 kids, but I am looking forward to all being together. We will get to see Grandparents, which will be nice but also a bit strange as we will be adhering to some social distancing. Overall, I am looking forward to our trip.
critical_positive: We had a lot in common and that allowed us to connect pretty quickly. My partner is from a state where I recently lived (for several years) and we have both traveled and lived in quite a few places. He had a good sense of humor and we were able to share lots of funny stories.
critical_negative: At first, I thought that we wouldn't have too much in common so it might be an awkward conversation. I also think that I was stereotyping him a bit without meaning to and felt like he was maybe going to be a bit judgemental, which really wasn't the case! The beginning felt a little bit 'forced' but after that things went really smoothly and it was genuinely an enjoyable conversation.
